title: ‘The Challenge’ Podcast Crossover Event With Aneesa and Tori | Death, Taxes, and Bananas
description:
Johnny is joined this week by ‘Challenge’ legends and hosts of ‘MTV’s Official Challenge Podcast’ Aneesa and Tori to talk about their careers, tell stories from their seasons together, discuss how the show has changed over the years, and a whole lot more.
Host: Johnny Bananas
Guests: Aneesa Ferreira and Tori Deal
Producers: Sasha Ashall and Devon Manze
